column5: boated 34 today,,the bass were just smashing the crankbaits,,,pitching tight wobbling cranks to shore and covering a ton of water,,the fish in the picture were kept in the livewell for the photo and were healthy as horses when released back to the lake
That's a lot of bass! Sounds like a fantastic day on the water .... Especially with that blue sky
Shorts and T shirts on Thanksgiving week-end! I bet it was just awesome out there!
Big numbers, I'm glad someone out there was getting some action!
Very fun day -- what lake did you fish?
